{"tid":1664402,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"死蠢請入","createTime":"2019-10-20T05:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T11:35:32.000Z","uid":328199,"like":5,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"32d53d1742fc3e539498ccd69ea7d123c5137d43","tid":1664402,"uid":328199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"重慶大廈俾支水你香港人<br />\n你哋就覺得佢哋係自己友<br />\n佢哋搶咗香港幾多資源知唔知<br />\n姦過殺過搶過幾多香港人你又知唔知<br />\n派下水就當冇事喇咩<br />\n咁林奠係咪派下錢就冇事呀<br />\n港豬清醒下喇dllm<br />\n佢哋收到風今日搞重慶先扮到咁咋<br />\n蝻想你哋拎支水幫佢哋爭取到香港人呢個身份咋<br />\n佢哋想我哋推翻個政權等特赦咋<br />\n屌你班傻鳩傻閪<br />\n咁低嘅智商點樣奪權<br />\n仆你個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534ffdbd233b429602cc0d9f31606dbb4db548c8","tid":1664402,"uid":51371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"咁你想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b254a635cbf9f94bb41d0f707b9005379a8cc30","tid":1664402,"uid":328199,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"534ffdbd233b429602cc0d9f31606dbb4db548c8","tid":1664402,"uid":51371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"咁你想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:36:58.000Z","msg":"你哋咁樣我哋取消行動都得喇<br />\nDllm"},{"pid":"4b014e77802ed5c417223d23c3ea573bd03e5892","tid":1664402,"uid":321856,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:40:50.000Z","msg":"分化撚"},{"pid":"05bf7ac2ee577e02b38fbbe43650d1e1accc19ce","tid":1664402,"uid":328199,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"唔怕負評<br />\n你駁到咪即管駁我<br />\n我係屌你哋呀死蠢<br />\n幾時先肯面對現實<br />\n幾時先肯用腦諗嘢<br />\n我要做企起身嗰個<br />\n但大部份族人仍然跪低<br />\n香港人<br />\n我對你哋好撚失望"},{"pid":"0650896c3e18657bc7f5fc1737ac66b0d5a5030e","tid":16